transcript:
Customer: As-salamu alaykum
Agent: Wa Alaikum Assalam, mein Ahmed bol raha hoon UBL se. Aap ki madad kese kar sakta hoon?
Agent: Zaroor, barah-e-karam apna TPIN batayen, chaar alag digits mein. Misal ke taur par: aik aik do do.
Agent: Shukriya. Ab barah-e-karam verification ke liye apna account number batayen.
Customer: eat, eat, eat, eat, eat, eat.
Agent: Aap ke account ka balance 0 hai. Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Agent: Maazrat, mein sirf account balance inquiry mein madad kar sakta hoon. Doosri services ke liye 111-825-888 per call karen ya apni qareeb tareen UBL
Customer: Bye.
Agent: branch visit karen. UBL call karne ka shukriya. Allah Hafiz!
